Thank you for updating to the latest NetBenefits app! Now you can:
•View the most recent contributions made by both you and your employer
•Answer a few questions to see how a small savings bump can affect your retirement
•Update your personal info

What’s New?
Thanks for updating your NetBenefits app! Now you can:
•Find out how much you may need to cover expenses in retirement
•Access your Fidelity Charitable Accounts
•View mutual fund library pages

Now you can do the following with the NetBenefits app:
•Register to access NetBenefits for the first time
•Reset your password
•Access international stock plans
•Update your account beneficiaries
•Get health & benefits alerts
*Note: If you have Touch ID enabled, you may be asked to set this feature again after the update.

•Our Send a Document feature is now compatible with iOS 11.
